title: Bonsai Finance Web App
description: Real-time stock analysis platform utilizing the AlphaVantage API, TwelveData API, and TradingView Widgets to deliver current stock data, sentiment insights, and historical analysis.

title: Portfolio Website
description: Next.js website displaying my portfolio and a little bit about myself. I used GSAP's scrollTrigger and useGSAP hook for the animations

title: Harvard Textbooks Scraper
description: Scrapes a google visualization table with textbooks and their info, converts it to a pandas dataframe, then writes the data to an excel file called 'output.xlsx'

title: Website for Cattrail Capital LLC
description: Website for a private investment company serving the Dekker family. Created using NextJS.

title: Twitter Sentiment Analysis
description: Scrapes Twitter for tweets about a given stock symbol, using Selenium WebDriver with Microsoft Edge, and performs sentiment analysis on the collected tweets using the TextBlob library.

title: Ad-Hoc BNF Specs Parser
description: Implemented OCaml types and Utop to build an ad-hoc parser for Backus-Naur form specifications. In the full project, we built a compiler/parser/evaluator from scratch.
